---
layout: layouts/app.njk
title: "Keyboard shortcuts"
description: "Every keyboard shortcut in Project Budget — global, navigation, register, modal, and command-palette."
permalink: /app/shortcuts/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<div class="app-page">
  <header class="app-page__header">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Keyboard</p>
      <h1 class="app-page__title">Keyboard shortcuts</h1>
      <p class="app-page__lead">Every shortcut the app responds to. When in doubt, press <kbd>?</kbd> to open the command palette — most actions are searchable there.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="card">
    <h2 class="card__title">Global</h2>
    <dl class="shortcuts-list">
      <div><dt><kbd>?</kbd></dt><dd>Open the command palette / search</dd></div>
      <div><dt><kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>K</kbd> <span class="shortcuts-list__or">or</span> <kbd>Cmd</kbd> + <kbd>K</kbd></dt><dd>Open the command palette / search</dd></div>
      <div><dt><kbd>N</kbd></dt><dd>Open the Quick Add transaction modal (outside any input)</dd></div>
      <div><dt><kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>Z</kbd> <span class="shortcuts-list__or">or</span> <kbd>Cmd</kbd> + <kbd>Z</kbd></dt><dd>Undo the last data mutation (skipped while typing)</dd></div>
      <div><dt><kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>Z</kbd></dt><dd>Redo</dd></div>
      <div><dt><kbd>Esc</kbd></dt><dd>Close any open modal, palette, or sidebar</dd></div>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <section class="card" style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
    <h2 class="card__title">Modal &amp; dialog</h2>
    <dl class="shortcuts-list">
      <div><dt><kbd>Tab</kbd> / <kbd>Shift</kbd>+<kbd>Tab</kbd></dt><dd>Move focus through fields; trapped inside the dialog while it's open</dd></div>
      <div><dt><kbd>Enter</kbd></dt><dd>Submit the form / confirm the action</dd></div>
      <div><dt><kbd>Esc</kbd></dt><dd>Cancel + close the dialog</dd></div>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <section class="card" style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
    <h2 class="card__title">Register</h2>
    <dl class="shortcuts-list">
      <div><dt><kbd>Enter</kbd></dt><dd>Commit the row being edited / open the next field</dd></div>
      <div><dt><kbd>Esc</kbd></dt><dd>Cancel the current edit without saving</dd></div>
      <div><dt><kbd>Tab</kbd></dt><dd>Move to the next cell in the row</dd></div>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <section class="card" style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
    <h2 class="card__title">Inline edits (payee rename, category rename, etc.)</h2>
    <dl class="shortcuts-list">
      <div><dt><kbd>Enter</kbd></dt><dd>Commit the new name</dd></div>
      <div><dt><kbd>Esc</kbd></dt><dd>Discard the change</dd></div>
      <div><dt>Click outside</dt><dd>Commit the new name (same as Enter)</dd></div>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <section class="card" style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
    <h2 class="card__title">Command palette</h2>
    <dl class="shortcuts-list">
      <div><dt><kbd>↑</kbd> / <kbd>↓</kbd></dt><dd>Move through results</dd></div>
      <div><dt><kbd>Enter</kbd></dt><dd>Run the highlighted command / open the highlighted result</dd></div>
      <div><dt>Type "<code>?</code>"</dt><dd>Force a docs search (skip the action list)</dd></div>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <section class="card" style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
    <h2 class="card__title">Calculator inputs (amount fields)</h2>
    <dl class="shortcuts-list">
      <div><dt><code>12.50 + 8.99</code></dt><dd>Type expressions; they evaluate on save</dd></div>
      <div><dt><code>100 - 25 * 2</code></dt><dd>Standard operator precedence</dd></div>
      <div><dt><code>(50)</code></dt><dd>Parentheses around a number = negative (accounting convention)</dd></div>
    </dl>
  </section>
</div>

<style>
  .shortcuts-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-2xs); margin: 0; }
  .shortcuts-list > div { display: grid; grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.5fr); align-items: baseline; padding: var(--space-2xs) 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft); gap: var(--space-md); }
  .shortcuts-list > div:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .shortcuts-list dt { margin: 0; }
  .shortcuts-list dd { margin: 0; color: var(--fg-muted); }
  .shortcuts-list kbd {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius-input);
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 0 0 var(--border-strong);
  }
  .shortcuts-list__or { color: var(--fg-muted); font-size: var(--fs-xs); padding: 0 var(--space-2xs); }
  .shortcuts-list code { font-family: var(--font-mono, ui-monospace, monospace); font-size: 0.85rem; background: var(--bg-alt); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; }
</style>
